  <bioghist encodinganalog="545"> 
	 <head>Historical Note</head> 
	 <p>This movement opposed policies of Hopi Tribal Council, Peabody Coal
		Company, Indian Claims Commission, and others which threatened traditional Hopi
		land and life.</p> 
  </bioghist> 
